00:08:37.669 --> 00:08:40.580
I'll later put this into
emotional intelligence.

00:08:40.580 --> 00:08:43.190
Empathetic listening are
very much about being--

00:08:43.190 --> 00:08:43.690
yes?

00:08:43.690 --> 00:08:45.620
AUDIENCE: Stay
calm during crisis.

00:08:45.620 --> 00:08:47.120
NADIM SAAD: Stay
calm during crisis.

