00:42:48.530 --> 00:42:51.500
is in itself--

00:42:51.500 --> 00:42:53.840
I mean, ideally you move
away from negotiating

00:42:53.840 --> 00:42:55.280
with your children.

00:42:55.280 --> 00:42:56.870
Because otherwise
everything turns out

00:42:56.870 --> 00:42:59.340
and turns into a negotiation.

00:42:59.340 --> 00:43:01.310
So what we want is
actually for them

00:43:01.310 --> 00:43:03.080
to have a sense of control.

00:43:03.080 --> 00:43:04.010
That's crucial.

00:43:04.010 --> 00:43:07.417
That's so for them
not to be a two

00:43:07.417 --> 00:43:09.500
and just be resistant and
not want to do anything.

00:43:09.500 --> 00:43:11.490
But so giving them
limited choices.

00:43:11.490 --> 00:43:14.950
So for example, do you
want your milk cold or hot?

00:43:14.950 --> 00:43:19.010
So you're anticipating the
issue before she tells you oh, I

00:43:19.010 --> 00:43:20.390
want my milk hot actually.

00:43:20.390 --> 00:43:22.400
So you allow her
to make decisions

00:43:22.400 --> 00:43:25.400
based on limited choices,
that will be usually helpful.

00:43:25.400 --> 00:43:26.570
But you do not negotiate.

00:43:26.570 --> 00:43:29.495
And then if it's actually she
decided she wanted it cold.

00:43:29.495 --> 00:43:31.370
And she then goes no,
actually I want it hot.

00:43:31.370 --> 00:43:34.100
Just like oh, next time Darling.

00:43:34.100 --> 00:43:36.390
Today you decided cold.

00:43:36.390 --> 00:43:39.480
Because otherwise
it's her way for--

00:43:39.480 --> 00:43:40.889
it's her way to control you.

00:43:40.889 --> 00:43:42.680
Because they do have
this need for control.

00:43:42.680 --> 00:43:46.100
So don't get me wrong,
it's totally normal.

00:43:46.100 --> 00:43:47.045
It's age appropriate.

00:43:47.045 --> 00:43:48.920
But you want to teach
them that they can have

00:43:48.920 --> 00:43:50.360
control, but on your terms.

00:43:50.360 --> 00:43:53.134
Otherwise they're
running the show.

00:43:53.134 --> 00:43:55.550
And then you've got a really
difficult life because it all

00:43:55.550 --> 00:43:57.990
turns out into a negotiation.

00:43:57.990 --> 00:44:00.865
So limited choices,
asking questions,

00:44:00.865 --> 00:44:02.240
and enforceable
statements, which

00:44:02.240 --> 00:44:03.864
is another one I
